	* lib/gnutls_ui.c, lib/x509/dn.c, lib/x509/pkcs7.c,
	lib/x509/pkcs7.h, lib/x509/x509.c: Null, as the data value, is now
	an acceptable value in functions that may return the size of the
	data.

