	* lib/Makefile.am: [no log message]

2003-02-07  nmav <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* NEWS, doc/tex/Makefile.am, doc/tex/certificate.tex,
	doc/tex/ex-rfc2818.tex, doc/tex/funcs.tex, includes/gnutls/x509.h,
