2002-06-22  nmav <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* libextra/gnutls_openpgp.c: [no log message]

2002-06-22  nmav <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* lib/auth_cert.c, lib/auth_dhe.c, lib/auth_rsa.c,
	lib/gnutls_cert.h, lib/gnutls_record.c, lib/gnutls_str.h,
	lib/gnutls_x509.c, lib/gnutls_x509.h: The TLS handshake no longer
	fails if the X.509 extensions in the Certificate are critical and
	unsupported. The unsupported critical extensions are now only
	catched by the verification functions.

