	functions

2001-06-01  nmav <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* NEWS, configure.in, lib/defines.h, lib/gnutls_cipher.c,
	lib/gnutls_handshake.c, lib/gnutls_num.c, lib/gnutls_num.h,
	src/prime.c: gnutls now handles uint64 even in systems without a
	native one.  several bug fixes.

